Finally, after a long and competitive 2 rounds of voting, three
council members have been chosen. Congratulations to you guys (and
gal)! If you login on the site, you'll see some council features there
for you.

The winners are: *drummroll*

Megan!   *clap clap clap*
rAuq!    *clap clap clap*
Alloran! *clap clap clap*

It was a tight race, but we finally got a few winners. THe poll is
still up, but you can't vote at it, its just there to check the
results at. Congratulations to the new council members!
